00:30:09,740 --> 00:30:11,230
Dalam katil bunga ini,

737
00:30:11,230 --> 00:30:13,300
Saya akan menanam
semua bunga kegemaran saya.

738
00:30:13,300 --> 00:30:14,260
Saya akan tanam

739
00:30:14,260 --> 00:30:15,470
hidrangea,

740
00:30:15,470 --> 00:30:16,740
Mawar Cina,

741
00:30:16,740 --> 00:30:17,740
bunga loceng,

742
00:30:17,740 --> 00:30:18,970
dan tomato ceri.

743
00:30:20,060 --> 00:30:21,390
Dan juga...

744
00:30:21,390 --> 00:30:22,230
Dan awak.

745
00:30:22,440 --> 00:30:24,100
Saya akan tanam awak di sini juga.

746
00:30:31,500 --> 00:30:34,420
(Kafe Internet Yingxiong)

747
00:30:41,190 --> 00:30:43,470
Chen Hui, datang ke sini sebentar.

748
00:30:45,780 --> 00:30:46,620
Pejam mata.

749
00:30:50,870 --> 00:30:51,750
Okay.

750
00:30:51,760 --> 00:30:52,750
Anda boleh membukanya sekarang.

751
00:30:55,020 --> 00:30:55,880
Bagaimana?

752
00:30:55,900 --> 00:30:56,750
Adakah ia kelihatan baik?

753
00:30:57,580 --> 00:30:58,420
Ia kelihatan hebat.

754
00:31:01,820 --> 00:31:02,660
terima kasih.

755
00:31:03,630 --> 00:31:04,580
Ia bukan apa-apa.

756
00:31:05,820 --> 00:31:07,540
Ini adalah permulaan baru kami.

757
00:31:07,540 --> 00:31:09,660
(Yingxiong)

758
00:31:13,190 --> 00:31:15,870
Saya akan buat.

759
00:31:15,870 --> 00:31:17,230
Ayah,

760
00:31:17,230 --> 00:31:18,300
berehat sebentar.

761
00:31:18,300 --> 00:31:19,670
Lihat sahaja dari sini.

762
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:20,920
Ayuh.

763
00:31:21,200 --> 00:31:22,210
Baiklah, mari kita pergi.

764
00:31:23,300 --> 00:31:24,500
Apa yang menjadi kekecohan sekarang?

765
00:31:25,240 --> 00:31:26,150
Biar saya buat.

766
00:31:26,150 --> 00:31:26,990
Ayah, izinkan saya.

767
00:31:26,990 --> 00:31:28,670
- Saya boleh uruskan.
- Hanya duduk. Duduklah.

768
00:31:28,670 --> 00:31:29,740
Bukankah ini bahan daripada

769
00:31:29,740 --> 00:31:30,670
bila Hui sakit?

770
00:31:30,670 --> 00:31:33,060
Ia menyukarkan pemandangan dan mengambil ruang,
jadi saya bersihkan semuanya.

771
00:31:33,060 --> 00:31:34,230
Senang nak kemas.

772
00:31:41,230 --> 00:31:42,080
Tang.

773
00:31:42,100 --> 00:31:42,940
Pengarah Chen.

774
00:31:43,920 --> 00:31:45,580
Saya di sini untuk mengemas kini anda
mengenai kes Gao Ying.

775
00:31:45,590 --> 00:31:46,430
Di sini.

776
00:31:46,820 --> 00:31:48,740
Keputusan bedah siasat Gao Ying
sudah keluar, kan?

777
00:31:48,740 --> 00:31:49,580
ya.

778
00:31:49,580 --> 00:31:51,230
Walaupun jenazah dikebumikan sekian lama

779
00:31:51,230 --> 00:31:52,950
bukti sebanyak itu
telah dimusnahkan secara biologi,

780
00:31:52,950 --> 00:31:54,230
kami jumpa serbuk

781
00:31:54,230 --> 00:31:56,060
pada badan,
dan ia adalah kalium manganat.

782
00:31:56,060 --> 00:31:57,540
Ia adalah bahan yang sama yang terdapat pada

783
00:31:57,540 --> 00:31:58,740
Mayat Yu Susu dan Lu Yuan.

784
00:31:59,230 --> 00:32:00,300
Itu berita indah.

785
00:32:01,500 --> 00:32:02,340
Tang,

786
00:32:02,710 --> 00:32:05,070
apa pendapat PSB perbandaran
tentang penggabungan kes?

787
00:32:05,190 --> 00:32:06,060
PSB perbandaran berkata

788
00:32:06,060 --> 00:32:07,580
kini ada langsung
bukti fizikal menghubungkan

789
00:32:07,580 --> 00:32:08,910
Kes Gao Ying kepada kes Huo Kaiming.

790
00:32:08,910 --> 00:32:10,740
Kita boleh mulakan prosesnya
daripada penggabungan kes.

791
00:32:11,230 --> 00:32:12,070
Tang,

792
00:32:12,500 --> 00:32:13,340
terima kasih.

793
00:32:13,340 --> 00:32:14,180
Baiklah.

794
00:32:17,950 --> 00:32:19,470
Pergi ambil rebusan daging kambing tu.

795
00:32:19,470 --> 00:32:20,310
Saya ada berita baik.

796
00:32:20,500 --> 00:32:21,470
Berita baik apa?

797
00:32:22,510 --> 00:32:24,780
Keputusan bedah siasat Gao Ying telah keluar.

798
00:32:24,780 --> 00:32:26,300
Ia bukan pembakaran spontan.

799
00:32:26,410 --> 00:32:27,670
Kami akhirnya menemui bukti,

800
00:32:27,680 --> 00:32:28,780
supaya kita boleh menggabungkan kes.

801
00:32:28,800 --> 00:32:29,990
Itu benar-benar berita baik.

802
00:32:29,990 --> 00:32:31,580
Baiklah. Saya akan pergi rebus daging kambing.

803
00:32:31,580 --> 00:32:32,420
Okay.

804
00:32:32,670 --> 00:32:33,540
Ayah,

805
00:32:33,540 --> 00:32:34,780
kita makan daging kambing malam ni.

806
00:32:36,020 --> 00:32:36,990
bagus.

807
00:32:36,990 --> 00:32:37,830
Ayah,

808
00:32:38,190 --> 00:32:39,030
jom masuk dalam.

809
00:32:39,740 --> 00:32:40,580
Jom masuk.

810
00:32:42,340 --> 00:32:44,630
beritahu saya,
adakah penjenayah itu telah ditangkap?

811
00:32:44,790 --> 00:32:46,540
Kami masih

812
00:32:46,540 --> 00:32:47,430
selepas penjenayah.

813
00:32:48,560 --> 00:32:49,430
Menangkap penjenayah

814
00:32:49,430 --> 00:32:50,870
adalah seperti menerbangkan layang-layang.

815
00:32:50,870 --> 00:32:53,260
Semakin kuat angin,
semakin banyak anda perlu melepaskan talian.

816
00:32:53,260 --> 00:32:54,100
Itulah yang mereka panggil

817
00:32:54,110 --> 00:32:55,510
"mengimbangi ketegangan dan kelonggaran".

818
00:32:56,100 --> 00:32:58,710
Jika tidak, tali wau akan putus.

819
00:32:58,710 --> 00:32:59,630
Perkara yang anda huraikan

820
00:32:59,630 --> 00:33:00,820
ialah cara menangkap ikan.

821
00:33:03,990 --> 00:33:04,990
Saya dah cakap

822
00:33:04,990 --> 00:33:06,150
Saya pasti akan

823
00:33:06,330 --> 00:33:07,910
sampai ke bahagian bawah kes ini.

824
00:33:07,910 --> 00:33:08,750
Nampak?

825
00:33:09,630 --> 00:33:10,910
Itu pasti.

826
00:33:10,910 --> 00:33:12,820
Apabila bercakap tentang kes,
awak tak pernah salah.

827
00:33:13,570 --> 00:33:14,740
Anda pasti mempunyai mata yang baik.

828
00:33:15,390 --> 00:33:16,430
Cukuplah.

829
00:33:16,430 --> 00:33:17,670
Pujian lagi akan menjadi terlalu banyak.

830
00:33:21,020 --> 00:33:22,100
Kenapa saya rasa macam

831
00:33:22,870 --> 00:33:24,300
anda telah menambah berat badan kebelakangan ini?

832
00:33:25,470 --> 00:33:26,310
Itu mustahil.

833
00:33:27,260 --> 00:33:28,710
Kes belum selesai.

834
00:33:28,710 --> 00:33:29,910
Bagaimana saya boleh menjadi gemuk?

835
00:33:33,230 --> 00:33:34,100
Saya masih ingat ketika itu,

836
00:33:34,100 --> 00:33:36,260
ketika saya mula-mula bertemu dengan awak,

837
00:33:36,260 --> 00:33:37,500
anda kelihatan agak cergas.

838
00:33:38,630 --> 00:33:39,980
Usah memikirkan kegemilangan masa lalu.

839
00:33:42,230 --> 00:33:43,500
Pada masa itu,

840
00:33:43,500 --> 00:33:45,300
anda memakai rambut anda dalam dua tocang kecil.

841
00:33:45,300 --> 00:33:46,470
Ia benar-benar cukup cantik.

842
00:33:47,150 --> 00:33:48,260
Anda masih ingat?

843
00:33:48,260 --> 00:33:49,300
Bagaimana saya boleh lupa?

844
00:33:51,100 --> 00:33:52,670
Rasanya

845
00:33:52,670 --> 00:33:54,710
itu lebih 20 tahun yang lalu.

846
00:33:57,340 --> 00:33:58,180
Hei, perempuan.

847
00:33:58,870 --> 00:34:01,470
Jom saya tengok
pada lencana Pengerusi Mao anda.

848
00:34:01,470 --> 00:34:02,330
Mari kita pinjam

849
00:34:02,330 --> 00:34:03,340
dan melihatnya.

850
00:34:03,780 --> 00:34:04,740
awak buat apa?

851
00:34:04,740 --> 00:34:05,700
- Apa yang kita buat?
- Apa yang kita buat?

852
00:34:05,710 --> 00:34:07,020
Berikan sahaja di sini!

853
00:34:07,470 --> 00:34:08,350
awak buat apa?

854
00:34:08,350 --> 00:34:09,540
Berhenti!

855
00:34:09,540 --> 00:34:10,380
Berhenti.

856
00:34:12,180 --> 00:34:13,020
Anda memintanya!

857
00:34:16,350 --> 00:34:18,140
Kembalikan! bergerak!

858
00:34:18,140 --> 00:34:18,990
Anda sangat berani.

859
00:34:18,990 --> 00:34:19,830
gerakkannya!

860
00:34:21,540 --> 00:34:22,390
Sesat!

861
00:34:22,530 --> 00:34:23,510
Apa kejadahnya?

862
00:34:24,700 --> 00:34:25,540
awak okay tak?

863
00:34:25,950 --> 00:34:26,790
saya sihat.

864
00:34:27,350 --> 00:34:28,190
terima kasih.

865
00:34:45,310 --> 00:34:46,170
Tunggu sekejap.

866
00:34:46,180 --> 00:34:47,070
Adakah anda masih ingat?

867
00:34:47,990 --> 00:34:49,270
Ketika itu, Gao Ying

868
00:34:50,020 --> 00:34:51,660
sentiasa mempunyai cahaya pelangi ini
atas kepalanya.

869
00:34:52,660 --> 00:34:53,790
Apabila matahari melandanya,

870
00:34:53,790 --> 00:34:54,700
semuanya berwarna-warni.

871
00:34:54,700 --> 00:34:55,540
Ia kelihatan agak bagus.

872
00:34:56,830 --> 00:34:57,670
saya tak ingat.

873
00:34:59,870 --> 00:35:00,710
Adakah anda marah?

874
00:35:02,620 --> 00:35:03,700
Saya hanya bertanya.

875
00:35:03,700 --> 00:35:04,540
apa salahnya

876
00:35:05,970 --> 00:35:06,830
ya.

877
00:35:06,830 --> 00:35:08,020
Ketika itu, dia sering mengalami

878
00:35:08,020 --> 00:35:09,100
cahaya atau sesuatu

879
00:35:09,100 --> 00:35:11,100
di rambutnya atau di badannya.

880
00:35:11,100 --> 00:35:13,020
Saya bertanya kepadanya mengenainya sekali kemudian.

881
00:35:13,020 --> 00:35:14,040
Dia berkata

882
00:35:14,060 --> 00:35:14,950
itu kerana ayahnya

883
00:35:14,970 --> 00:35:16,990
bekerja di kilang basuh arang batu lama.

884
00:35:16,990 --> 00:35:19,310
Dia sering pergi ke sana
untuk membawakan dia makanan.

885
00:35:19,310 --> 00:35:20,870
Setiap kali dia pulang dari situ,

886
00:35:20,870 --> 00:35:22,060
pada badannya

887
00:35:22,060 --> 00:35:23,870
dan di rambutnya,
akan ada cahaya itu.

888
00:35:23,870 --> 00:35:25,580
Nampaknya

889
00:35:25,580 --> 00:35:27,470
daripada air di kolam basuh arang batu.

890
00:35:30,140 --> 00:35:31,580
Loji basuh arang batu lama.

891
00:35:45,740 --> 00:35:55,540
(Loji Pencuci Arang Heyi, Bandar Fengyang)

892
00:36:16,750 --> 00:36:17,590
Apa ini?

893
00:36:23,470 --> 00:36:24,310
Sebuah motosikal.

894
00:36:29,220 --> 00:36:30,180
Ia kelihatan seperti

895
00:36:30,180 --> 00:36:31,350
yang diterangkan oleh Ma Heping.

896
00:36:32,950 --> 00:36:34,430
Adakah wanita berparut itu?

897
00:36:34,430 --> 00:36:35,620
Sangat berkemungkinan.

898
00:36:35,620 --> 00:36:36,500
Pergi.

899
00:36:36,500 --> 00:36:37,340
Lihatlah sekeliling.

900
00:37:07,910 --> 00:37:08,750
dengan pantas.

901
00:37:09,470 --> 00:37:10,310
Pergi cari tiang.

902
00:37:10,870 --> 00:37:11,710
Okay.

903
00:37:21,220 --> 00:37:22,700
Pengarah Chen.

904
00:37:34,180 --> 00:37:35,310
Ada sesuatu di bawah.

905
00:37:37,220 --> 00:37:38,540
Ia agak berat.

906
00:37:38,540 --> 00:37:39,380
Beri saya tangan.

907
00:37:44,390 --> 00:37:45,230
Buka dan lihat.

908
00:37:53,350 --> 00:37:54,310
Ada satu lagi lapisan.

909
00:38:03,430 --> 00:38:04,270
Ia adalah sirap batuk.

910
00:38:04,860 --> 00:38:07,700
(Sirap Batuk Peidun)

911
00:38:07,700 --> 00:38:08,830
Ia penuh dengan mereka.

